{"tid":1114764,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"尋一首舊廣東歌","createTime":"2019-04-18T16:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T17:19:35.000Z","uid":144126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e2efb645f1cadf83830aa0d3bd582fae11aafc","tid":1114764,"uid":144126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:17:19.000Z","msg":"有首歌以前間唔時聽到但唔記得曲名<br />\n依家每次聽到就成日諗住google 返歌名<br />\n但次次都老人痴呆轉頭就唔記得keyword<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大概九十年代，女聲，好似兩三合唱，<br />\n內容大意好似講姊妹間唔一定要完全理念一致但會相互支持咁<br />\n<br />\n我自己都知1999同提示好空泛<br />\n但希望有巴絲解到小弟呢個up到咀邊又成日唔就記得嘅心結<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82db2f34765973de18bdcbefa5f53c4548f7ba5b","tid":1114764,"uid":111644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望你搵到"},{"pid":"672691b94a04c581882ce45c3dd4c0a0907700c2","tid":1114764,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"2R - 我們的合唱歌"},{"pid":"871edeea3a782db2433390f79498fc7bda65687a","tid":1114764,"uid":144126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"672691b94a04c581882ce45c3dd4c0a0907700c2","tid":1114764,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"2R - 我們的合唱歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔係呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印象中好似小恩子定靚湯嗰類舊啲嘅歌手<br />\n<br />\nBtw,thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac0baa8fd6f0259065103baf7838dc8d8b4dffa","tid":1114764,"uid":182707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"一人有一個理想<br />\n作曲/編曲/監製: 陳光榮<br />\n填詞: 黃偉文<br />\n主唱: 黎瑞恩, 羅敏莊, 杜雯惠, Vani"},{"pid":"3443a05993f6194c6dc8b58e3f0612d7ef2e0daf","tid":1114764,"uid":182707,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quot